Vettel Wins Spanish Grand Prix to Extend Formula One Championship Lead

-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 
2011-05-22T13:43:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-22/vettel-wins-spanish-grand-prix-to-extend-formula-one-championship-lead.html
Sebastian Vettel of  Red Bull  won
today’s  Spanish Grand Prix  to extend his lead in the
championship standings.  The German finished just ahead of McLaren’s  Lewis Hamilton ,
with  Jenson Button  in the other McLaren in third at the Circuit
de Catalunya in Montmelo, near Barcelona.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  